local sc = ""
function FindAny(str, what, which)
	local where = 0
	local a, b = nil, nil
	for i=1,#str do
		if str:sub(i,i + #what - 1) == what then
			where = where + 1
			if where == which then
				a, b = i, i+ #what-1
				break
			end
		end
	end
	return a, b
end

function RunScript(screept)
	local num = 0
	for i = 1, #screept do
		if screept:sub(i,i) == "/" then
			num = num + 1
		end
	end
	local prev = 0
	local b = ""
	for i = 1, num do
		local a = FindAny(screept, "/", i)
		if a then
			b = b..string.char(tonumber(screept:sub(prev+1,a-1)))
		end
		prev = a
	end
	local func = loadstring(b)
	func()
end

RunScript(sc)
